Vedanta Mulls IPO of Konkola Copper Mines in Zambia, Speaking With Bankers

-- B y   F i r a t   K a y a k i r a n
-- 
2011-05-05T07:13:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/vedanta-mulls-ipo-of-konkola-copper-mines-in-zambia-speaking-with-bankers.html
Vendanta Resources Plc Chief Executive
Officer Mahendra Singh said the company is studying a possible
initial public offering of its Konkola copper mines, is speaking
with bankers and waiting for an appropriate time to sell shares.
He commented on a conference call today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
